‚≠ź What is Kubernetes?
Kubernetes (K8s) is an open-source container orchestration platform used to:
	‚ÄĘ Deploy applications
	‚ÄĘ Scale applications
	‚ÄĘ Load balance traffic
	‚ÄĘ Restart failed containers
	‚ÄĘ Rollout & rollback new versions
	‚ÄĘ Manage cluster resources
It automates deployment, scaling, and management of containerized applications.

ūüßĪ Why Kubernetes? (Benefits)
	‚ÄĘ Self-healing (restarts crashed containers)
	‚ÄĘ Auto-scaling
	‚ÄĘ Rolling updates
