ūüü¶ Kubernetes Architecture (Easy + Complete)
Kubernetes has two main parts:
1ÔłŹ‚É£ Control Plane (Master Node) ‚Üí Brain of the cluster
2ÔłŹ‚É£ Worker Nodes ‚Üí Run your applications
Think of it like:
	‚ÄĘ Master = Manager
